Uses of Package
gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.instance

  • Packages that use gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.instance 
    Package Description
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.io.context  
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.model
    Provides the core implementation of the Metaschema model (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common) represented as Java class annotations (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.model.annotations).
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.model.annotations
    Provides a set of annotations for associating Metaschema information with a Java class.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.model.property  
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.codegen.property  
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common
    Provides interfaces, abstract implementation classes, and excptions that are used in Metaschema APIs.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.definition
    Representations of Metaschema model definitions.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.instance
    Representations of Metaschema model instances used in a Metaschema assembly or field.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.ast
    An implementation of an abstract syntax tree representation of a compiled Metapath expression.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.evaluate.instance
    Support for evaluating a Metapath expression against Metaschema definitions.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.format
    Support for defining and evaluating Metapath functions.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.util
    Various utilities and helper methods.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.definitions  
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.instances  
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.xml
    An implementation of the Metaschema model (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common) using an underlying XML format.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.xmlbeans
    XMLBeans generated classes for the Metaschema XML format.
    gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.xmlbeans.handler
    XMLBeans generated class binding data type handlers for the Metaschema XML format.
